The "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" course offered by 4Geeks Academy is a 16-week program designed for individuals with no previous knowledge in the field. The course helps students start a career as a data scientist and build their first machine learning models. Taught by experienced instructors, including Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena, the course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy, explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and work with supervised and unsupervised learning models. The course also emphasizes real-life case studies, industry-standard tools, and the development, deployment, and maintenance of AI projects. The program offers certificates recognized by multiple organizations and is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop